NAME

Lingua-FR-Ladl - a set of modules to represent, query and investigate the Ladl
tables, a french linguistic resource, distributed as a set of excel tables.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

Class::Std
List::Util
List::MoreUtils

and

XML::LibXML if you want to load table data from a gnumeric XML file
Spreadsheet::ParseExcel if you want to load table data from an excel file
DBI - if you want to use the DB interface


